{"tid":2463993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TVB推出「楊明」新劇, 對憾MIRROR陳卓賢新劇","createTime":"2021-03-27T06:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T06:53:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"089de22da01077513e4574e53391a914506ce44e","tid":2463993,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:33:48.000Z","msg":"ViuTV會係4月5日晚上9:30推出由MIRROR陳卓賢主演的《無限斜棟有限公司》.  <br />\nCCTVB當然不敢怠慢, 係4月12日晚上9:30推出由多名藍絲偽人主演既《伙記辦大事》.<br />\n(兩套劇都出左宣傳)<br />\n<br />\n《伙記辦大事》演員陣容: 楊明、 歐陽震華、 馬蹄露 (<strong>三名演員也曾公開支持香港國安法</strong>)<br />\n《無限斜棟有限公司》演員陣容: 陳卓賢、黃定謙、盧慧敏、葉 童、吳家麗、太 保、袁富華、葛民輝、蘇麗珊、區嘉雯、黃光亮、張建聲、何華超  <br />\n<br />\n《伙記辦大事》有咁多藍絲偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 反而《無限斜棟有限公司》除左陳卓賢, 仲有唔少金像影星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 正常香港人都識揀啦.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《無限斜棟有限公司》分半鐘 trailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PL0vWiVF1xU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPL0vWiVF1xU&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=aaf00697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PL0vWiVF1xU</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmazNRnpWZ8WxtLFGfvcxmjUJ3aHxH2vX94RCLP1Dg9EyQ?filename=Rzz7mkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzz7mkB.jpg&h=4dcbc369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e90f4de08af79ea8c362697618949385e507759","tid":2463993,"uid":134071,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"再重複: 歐陽震華支持香港國安法<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme3R3aGEo35KvEySGbDFSLtL4CgkfjFkuVtdcK967Dbxn?filename=0za4bWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0za4bWv.png&h=81049acc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af5de69bd1e08b0e9ad683a6ab758429c4cacd7e","tid":2463993,"uid":134071,"like":5,"di